data.description: 17.82 ACRE!!!!+ 3 bedroom/2 bath home with unfinished basement, oversized 2 car attached garage and a 22x23 detached garage. Some great features of this home are a covered front and back porch that have gorgeous farm views! New LG Kitchen appliances stay in addition to the washer and dryer. Newer carpet throughout and updated luxury vinyl flooring in the kitchen. Abundance of wildlife runs through daily. Approx 5-7 acres are cleared and the remaining is all rolling and wooded. Sellers have cut out some paths to ride fourwheelers/side by sides. Centrally located between multiple boat ramps AND marinas. You can be to Lees Ford, Wolf Creek Marina, Cumberland Pointe, or Pulaski County Park within a few miles depending which direction you take. Great views, neighbors, and Rural location!
